listitem.para:
Axioms can also be edited at various hierarchical levels by selecting the
                        Pencil Icon next to the Axiom's concept and selecting the appropriate action
                        from the drop down menu ()

We can edit the T.O.M Pizza concept by following the steps outlined in the
                        Create a Concept section to add an additional role group, with a Role Type
                        for "Has Base", and Role Restriction of "Pizza Base" to our pizza concept ()
